						<a class="post_more_title" href="https://lithub.com/a-riveting-timeless-journey-through-the-afterlife-inside-the-world-of-dantes-divine-comedy/">
				<h4 style="margin:0">A Riveting, Timeless Journey Through the Afterlife: Inside the World of Dante’s <em>Divine Comedy</em></h4>
			</a>
			Go to the poetry section of any reasonably well-­stocked bookstore, and you will find Dante’s Divine Comedy represented...			
